drs = pd.read_csv("./DRS_tpm_samples.tsv",sep="\t",index_col=0)
drs = drs.reset_index()
drs_melt = drs.melt(id_vars="transcript_name")
drs_melt["gene_id"] = drs_melt["transcript_name"].map(lambda x: ref_dict.get(x))
drs_melt["tissues"] = drs_melt["variable"].str.replace(r'S\d+-','')
drs_gene_sample = drs_melt.groupby(["variable","gene_id"])["value"].agg('mean').to_frame()
drs_gene_tissue = drs_melt.groupby(["tissues","gene_id"])["value"].agg('mean').to_frame()
drs_gene_sample = drs_gene_sample.reset_index().pivot(columns="variable",index="gene_id",values="value")
drs_gene_tissue = drs_gene_tissue.reset_index().pivot(columns="tissues",index="gene_id",values="value")
drs_gene_sample.to_csv("./DRS_gene_tpm_samples.tsv",sep="\t")
drs_gene_tissue.to_csv("./DRS_gene_tpm_tissues.tsv",sep="\t")

ngs_tc_tpm = pd.read_csv("../NGS/NGS_tpm_samples.tsv",sep="\t",index_col=0)

drs_tc_tpm = pd.read_csv("./DRS_tpm_samples.tsv",sep="\t",index_col=0)

merged_df = ngs_tc_tpm.join(drs_tc_tpm,rsuffix="_DRS")

from scipy import stats

tc_corr = []
for sample in drs_tc_tpm.columns:
    plot_sample = merged_df[[sample,sample+"_DRS"]].fillna(0)
    plot_sample = np.log10(plot_sample[(plot_sample>1).sum(axis=1)>1])
    corr = round(stats.pearsonr(plot_sample[sample],  plot_sample[sample+"_DRS"]).correlation,2)
    tc_corr.append(corr)
In [20]:
name="S10-brain"
plot_sample = merged_df[[name,name+"_DRS"]].fillna(0)
# plot_sample = plot_sample.dropna()
plot_sample = np.log10(plot_sample[(plot_sample>1).sum(axis=1)>1])
corr = round(stats.pearsonr(plot_sample[name],  plot_sample[name+"_DRS"]).correlation,2)
plt.figure(figsize=(4,4))
sns.regplot(y = plot_sample[name], x= plot_sample[name+"_DRS"],color="#376795",scatter_kws={"s":8,"color":"#72BCD5"})
plt.title(name)
plt.ylabel("log10 (NGS TPM)")
plt.xlabel("log10 (Nanopore TPM )")
plt.text(0.5,4.5,f'R ={corr}')
plt.xlim(0,5)

p2 = pd.DataFrame()
for tissue in drs_estCount.columns:
    t1 = drs_estCount[[tissue]]
    t1 = t1.sort_values(by=tissue,ascending=False)
#     t1 = t1[t1[tissue] >0.5]
    t1["Percent"] = t1[tissue].cumsum()/t1[tissue].sum()
    t1["Percent"] = t1["Percent"]*100
    t1 = t1.reset_index().reset_index()
    t1["index"] = t1["index"] + 1
    t1.columns = ["index","geneid","value","Percent"]
    t1["tissues"] = tissue

    p2 = pd.concat([p2,t1])

In [51]:
DRS_topIsoforms = []
p3 = pd.DataFrame()
for tissue in drs_estCount.columns:
    t1 = drs_estCount[[tissue]]
    t1 = t1.sort_values(by=tissue,ascending=False)
    t1 = t1[t1[tissue] >0.1]
    t1["Percent"] = t1[tissue].cumsum()/t1[tissue].sum()
    t1["Percent"] = t1["Percent"]*100
    t1 = t1.reset_index(drop=True).reset_index()
    t1["index"] = t1["index"] + 1
    t1.columns = ["index","value","Percent"]
    t1["tissues"] = tissue
    print(t1.head(10000).tail(1))
    DRS_topIsoforms.append(t1.head(1000).tail(1)["Percent"].values[0])
    p3 = pd.concat([p3,t1])
